1
00:00:07,745 --> 00:00:09,025
SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:39,425 --> 00:01:43,065
ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
QUEEN CHU ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:01:46,145 --> 00:01:48,585
That day, blood stained the Palace walls.

4
00:01:50,065 --> 00:01:51,265
It showed me the truth.

5
00:01:52,385 --> 00:01:54,825
There's no real love in these halls.

6
00:01:55,905 --> 00:01:58,185
If fate grants me another chance,

7
00:01:58,265 --> 00:02:02,545
I would tell you of every misstep
and how they

8
00:02:03,705 --> 00:02:05,745
led to my ruin.

9
00:02:08,744 --> 00:02:10,505
‎YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

10
00:02:28,185 --> 00:02:29,665
Stop! Stop there!

11
00:02:29,745 --> 00:02:31,065
My horse!

12
00:02:34,065 --> 00:02:35,305
I'm Chu Zhao.

13
00:02:35,385 --> 00:02:38,345
I grew up in Yunzhong,
a desert prefecture.

14
00:02:38,425 --> 00:02:39,665
This is part of the frontier.

15
00:02:39,745 --> 00:02:41,825
Foes from the Northern Desert
often invade.

16
00:02:41,905 --> 00:02:43,345
My mother died when I was little.

17
00:02:43,425 --> 00:02:45,185
I've been living with my father.

18
00:02:45,265 --> 00:02:46,825
He's a frontier general

19
00:02:46,905 --> 00:02:48,945
who has served for over a decade.

20
00:02:49,025 --> 00:02:50,465
My impression of Mother is just

21
00:02:50,545 --> 00:02:53,225
what Father told me in my childhood.

22
00:02:53,305 --> 00:02:54,225
THE CAPITAL

23
00:02:54,305 --> 00:02:58,065
The Capital is where my mother
used to live.

24
00:02:58,145 --> 00:03:00,465
I longed so much to visit it,

25
00:03:00,545 --> 00:03:03,705
but my father forbade me
to leave Yunzhong.

26
00:03:03,785 --> 00:03:05,625
Now, I've grown up.

27
00:03:05,705 --> 00:03:07,185
I can gallop on a horse, too.

28
00:03:07,265 --> 00:03:08,185
He, all alone,

29
00:03:08,265 --> 00:03:09,785
stands against thousands of troops.

30
00:03:09,865 --> 00:03:12,505
That's how he subdued
the Northern Desert all alone!

31
00:03:13,105 --> 00:03:13,985
Brilliant!

32
00:03:14,825 --> 00:03:16,625
Miss. You're so pretty. Want a flower?

33
00:03:18,785 --> 00:03:19,905
One more!

34
00:03:20,505 --> 00:03:21,905
Carriages constantly move.

35
00:03:21,985 --> 00:03:23,105
People walk around.

36
00:03:23,905 --> 00:03:26,385
The city is crowded and bustling.

37
00:03:27,025 --> 00:03:30,185
When the scenes here
became vivid in front of me,

38
00:03:30,705 --> 00:03:32,305
I finally realized something.

39
00:03:33,265 --> 00:03:35,745
How I wish my mother were still alive.

40
00:03:38,065 --> 00:03:40,185
How I wish she could stay by my side,

41
00:03:40,785 --> 00:03:43,745
choosing hairpins
for my coming-of-age ceremony,

42
00:03:43,825 --> 00:03:46,585
and see what I've become.

43
00:03:46,665 --> 00:03:47,625
LOTUS PAVILION

44
00:03:49,625 --> 00:03:50,465
Go fight it!

45
00:03:53,105 --> 00:03:54,385
Go for it!

46
00:03:55,025 --> 00:03:58,385
-Good!
-Do it!

47
00:03:59,225 --> 00:04:00,705
Beat him! Kill him!

48
00:04:00,785 --> 00:04:01,625
-Beat him!
-Excuse me.

49
00:04:02,585 --> 00:04:04,065
Beat him!

50
00:04:04,825 --> 00:04:05,785
Beat hard!

51
00:04:24,345 --> 00:04:26,225
In broad daylight, how can you lynch him?

52
00:04:26,305 --> 00:04:27,945
Who are you, girl? Go away!

53
00:04:28,025 --> 00:04:29,105
He's terrible.

54
00:04:29,185 --> 00:04:32,545
Last night, he burned the Wei Village
and killed 46 people.

55
00:04:33,145 --> 00:04:34,385
Death is too good for him.

56
00:04:34,465 --> 00:04:35,585
Let's kill him.

57
00:04:35,665 --> 00:04:38,745
By law,
lynching is no different from murder.

58
00:04:39,425 --> 00:04:41,065
I've finally found you.

59
00:04:41,145 --> 00:04:42,465
Come on. Be good, will you?

60
00:04:42,545 --> 00:04:43,465
ZHONG CHANGRONG
DEPUTY GENERAL OF FRONTIER TROOPS

61
00:04:43,545 --> 00:04:45,225
-Sorry for this. Sorry.
-Mr. Zhong.

62
00:04:45,305 --> 00:04:47,385
They're killing him casually!

63
00:04:47,465 --> 00:04:48,305
Behave.

64
00:04:49,745 --> 00:04:50,585
Why do you stop me?

65
00:04:51,185 --> 00:04:53,185
-They're in the wrong.
-You…

66
00:04:53,265 --> 00:04:54,425
Without interrogation,

67
00:04:54,505 --> 00:04:56,825
they convicted him
and were trying to lynch him.

68
00:04:56,905 --> 00:04:57,945
Oh, you don't understand.

69
00:04:58,625 --> 00:05:01,705
Just stay out of the intricate affairs
of these big clans.

70
00:05:01,785 --> 00:05:03,545
Your father gave me an order.

71
00:05:03,625 --> 00:05:04,905
I must take you back.

72
00:05:04,985 --> 00:05:06,025
Let's go.

73
00:05:10,065 --> 00:05:12,145
Excuse me. Please let us through.

74
00:05:14,345 --> 00:05:15,545
Leave. Leave now.

75
00:05:16,065 --> 00:05:18,425
-Go away. Mind your own business.
-We can't let him go!

76
00:05:18,505 --> 00:05:20,425
Let's go.

77
00:05:20,505 --> 00:05:22,305
Come on.

78
00:05:25,185 --> 00:05:26,985
Not even a full day in the Chu capital,

79
00:05:27,065 --> 00:05:29,065
Mr. Zhong brought me back to Yunzhong.

80
00:05:29,705 --> 00:05:30,545
Just as I thought,

81
00:05:30,625 --> 00:05:31,465
MILITARY CAMP OF YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

82
00:05:31,545 --> 00:05:33,745
Father was furious that I ran off.

83
00:05:33,825 --> 00:05:36,505
Yunzhong is so far away from the Capital.

84
00:05:37,025 --> 00:05:38,665
Do you know how many bandits

85
00:05:38,745 --> 00:05:40,065
and enemies are out there?

86
00:05:40,785 --> 00:05:42,465
-What if--?
-What?

87
00:05:42,545 --> 00:05:44,905
Am I not standing here safe and sound?

88
00:05:44,985 --> 00:05:47,505
Why do you always want to trap me in here?

89
00:05:47,585 --> 00:05:48,785
CHU LING, THE GUARD GENERAL

90
00:05:48,865 --> 00:05:49,785
When I was in the Capital,

91
00:05:50,385 --> 00:05:52,145
I visited my uncle and my cousin.

92
00:05:52,865 --> 00:05:55,105
I also experienced local customs there.

93
00:05:55,185 --> 00:05:56,545
How ignorant you are!

94
00:05:57,185 --> 00:05:59,305
You only know the Capital
is your mother's hometown.

95
00:05:59,385 --> 00:06:00,945
Do you know it's also a devouring cage?

96
00:06:01,025 --> 00:06:04,225
Father, don't scare me.
I just missed my mother.

97
00:06:04,745 --> 00:06:05,825
I didn't grow up by her side,

98
00:06:05,905 --> 00:06:07,705
so I wanted to take a look.

99
00:06:08,385 --> 00:06:09,505
To look at the sights she saw

100
00:06:09,585 --> 00:06:11,425
and walk the lanes she walked.

101
00:06:12,305 --> 00:06:13,785
I wanted to find

102
00:06:13,865 --> 00:06:17,025
even the slightest trace
of my mother's existence.

103
00:06:17,105 --> 00:06:18,905
How dare you bring her up?

104
00:06:20,025 --> 00:06:22,665
If she knew you were being so willful,

105
00:06:22,745 --> 00:06:24,225
she would be heartbroken!

106
00:06:24,305 --> 00:06:26,345
I just try to live on my own terms.

107
00:06:26,425 --> 00:06:27,865
Does it make me willful?

108
00:06:27,945 --> 00:06:30,225
If Mother were still alive,

109
00:06:30,305 --> 00:06:32,665
she wouldn't want me
to be an obedient girl.

110
00:06:33,425 --> 00:06:35,185
She wouldn't be as arrogant as you.

111
00:06:36,145 --> 00:06:38,265
She would care about my feelings.

112
00:06:38,865 --> 00:06:39,825
Yeah.

113
00:06:40,865 --> 00:06:43,065
You're the undefeated God of War.

114
00:06:43,145 --> 00:06:45,465
You're the esteemed Guard General.

115
00:06:45,545 --> 00:06:48,585
But have you ever asked
if I wish to be a general's daughter?

116
00:06:49,745 --> 00:06:51,105
Since childhood,

117
00:06:51,625 --> 00:06:53,385
other girls have had parents around.

118
00:06:53,465 --> 00:06:54,545
What about me?

119
00:06:55,145 --> 00:06:57,065
I've always been neglected.

120
00:06:57,985 --> 00:07:00,505
Have I ever cried or complained to you?

121
00:07:00,585 --> 00:07:02,705
I've never dared
to ask you for a little concern.

122
00:07:02,785 --> 00:07:03,985
Because you've always been busy.

123
00:07:04,905 --> 00:07:06,385
You're busy protecting frontier people.

124
00:07:06,465 --> 00:07:08,945
You're busy forging your fame.

125
00:07:09,025 --> 00:07:10,265
You're too busy

126
00:07:10,345 --> 00:07:13,345
to ask your daughter
what she really wants!

127
00:07:25,385 --> 00:07:26,425
Lan,

128
00:07:27,385 --> 00:07:28,625
I'm sorry.

129
00:07:29,625 --> 00:07:31,785
I failed to take good care
of our daughter.

130
00:07:32,305 --> 00:07:35,625
All I can do now is grant her wish.

131
00:07:40,905 --> 00:07:44,265
CHU

132
00:07:44,345 --> 00:07:45,985
CHU MANSION

133
00:07:46,065 --> 00:07:49,465
What I said to Father
must have broken his heart.

134
00:07:49,545 --> 00:07:51,825
Otherwise, he wouldn't have sent me

135
00:07:51,905 --> 00:07:53,385
to the Capital as I always wished,

136
00:07:53,465 --> 00:07:56,065
to the Chu Mansion granted by His Majesty.

137
00:07:57,105 --> 00:07:59,465
I tried hard to learn manners,

138
00:07:59,545 --> 00:08:01,505
expecting to be a true noble lady

139
00:08:01,585 --> 00:08:03,825
in the Capital
as my father described my mother.

140
00:08:04,545 --> 00:08:07,625
I'd behave gracefully
and smile with lips closed.

141
00:08:09,305 --> 00:08:13,065
However, these things
were far harder than I ever imagined.

142
00:08:15,745 --> 00:08:17,505
The way I wanted to be

143
00:08:18,585 --> 00:08:20,785
turned out to be ridiculous.

144
00:08:21,825 --> 00:08:23,105
It was at that moment

145
00:08:24,145 --> 00:08:26,185
that I met Xun.

146
00:08:30,385 --> 00:08:31,865
How are the stars here,

147
00:08:31,945 --> 00:08:33,625
compared to those in the desert?

148
00:08:34,465 --> 00:08:35,745
Zhao.

149
00:08:35,825 --> 00:08:36,904
They're as beautiful.

150
00:08:45,665 --> 00:08:48,785
That was the first time he called my name.

151
00:08:49,305 --> 00:08:50,545
And just because of that,

152
00:08:51,065 --> 00:08:54,145
I finally felt
that the Capital had accepted me.

153
00:08:54,225 --> 00:08:58,065
Because someone here cared for me,
thought of me, and cherished me.

154
00:08:59,305 --> 00:09:02,785
Shortly after that,
Xun went to Yunzhong to propose.

155
00:09:09,465 --> 00:09:10,705
Zhao.

156
00:09:11,545 --> 00:09:12,745
The desert scenery

157
00:09:13,265 --> 00:09:14,505
is far grander than that of the Capital.

158
00:09:15,105 --> 00:09:16,465
It's been three years.

159
00:09:16,545 --> 00:09:17,865
You must have missed your hometown.

160
00:09:19,345 --> 00:09:20,465
Not really.

161
00:09:21,865 --> 00:09:23,945
Sand always swirls across the sky here.

162
00:09:24,945 --> 00:09:26,225
Seeing it too often

163
00:09:27,345 --> 00:09:28,305
makes it dull instead.

164
00:09:33,265 --> 00:09:35,145
You there, listen up!

165
00:09:35,225 --> 00:09:37,665
Give me all the valuables!

166
00:09:38,665 --> 00:09:40,665
Your Highness, we're ambushed.

167
00:09:45,905 --> 00:09:49,145
Be wise enough, and I'll let you live!

168
00:09:49,225 --> 00:09:52,265
Otherwise, I'll kill you all!

169
00:10:08,065 --> 00:10:09,665
Young man, who are you?

170
00:10:16,705 --> 00:10:18,425
FU JIU, CHU FAMILY'S RETAINER

171
00:10:18,505 --> 00:10:19,865
How noisy.

172
00:10:25,025 --> 00:10:26,985
Lads, go get him.

173
00:10:50,585 --> 00:10:51,665
Your Highness,

174
00:10:51,745 --> 00:10:53,385
I've never seen such fierce swordsmanship.

175
00:10:54,305 --> 00:10:55,665
Every strike is fatal.

176
00:11:04,825 --> 00:11:05,745
I'm Fu Jiu,

177
00:11:06,385 --> 00:11:07,545
working for General Chu.

178
00:11:08,545 --> 00:11:10,865
He sent me to kill the bandits.

179
00:11:14,185 --> 00:11:15,225
Help me, my lord!

180
00:11:16,465 --> 00:11:17,465
Stay back!

181
00:11:18,225 --> 00:11:19,865
Or I'll kill her.

182
00:11:36,345 --> 00:11:37,305
Are you insane?

183
00:11:37,385 --> 00:11:38,545
She's innocent.

184
00:11:47,505 --> 00:11:48,705
Foolish.

185
00:11:59,625 --> 00:12:00,945
Her bracelet

186
00:12:01,025 --> 00:12:03,625
and the chief's necklace
belong to the same set.

187
00:12:03,705 --> 00:12:04,785
Rare in the market.

188
00:12:05,425 --> 00:12:07,625
Just now, she deliberately
rushed out from behind.

189
00:12:08,625 --> 00:12:10,345
So, the bandit managed to seize her.

190
00:12:11,985 --> 00:12:14,705
Xun, before departure,

191
00:12:14,785 --> 00:12:17,465
did you verify the identity
of your attendants?

192
00:12:17,545 --> 00:12:18,985
The other day,

193
00:12:19,065 --> 00:12:21,585
I did notice some unfamiliar servants.

194
00:12:23,145 --> 00:12:24,265
But in a hurry,

195
00:12:24,785 --> 00:12:25,905
I didn't scrutinize.

196
00:12:29,545 --> 00:12:31,025
You were careless.

197
00:12:47,185 --> 00:12:49,225
YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

198
00:12:50,105 --> 00:12:52,785
I've sincerely come here
to propose to your daughter.

199
00:12:52,865 --> 00:12:54,345
Betrothal gifts are ready.

200
00:12:54,425 --> 00:12:55,545
Here is the list.

201
00:12:56,265 --> 00:12:57,985
Please review it.

202
00:13:00,545 --> 00:13:02,665
My daughter

203
00:13:03,505 --> 00:13:05,025
isn't good enough for a noble gentleman.

204
00:13:06,385 --> 00:13:07,225
Your Highness,

205
00:13:07,745 --> 00:13:09,505
I suggest you go back.

206
00:13:10,025 --> 00:13:13,385
Father, Xun and I love each other.

207
00:13:13,465 --> 00:13:14,705
What's wrong with his origin?

208
00:13:15,305 --> 00:13:16,465
If I can't marry him,

209
00:13:17,065 --> 00:13:17,945
why did you marry my mother,

210
00:13:18,025 --> 00:13:19,865
a noble young lady from far away?

211
00:13:19,945 --> 00:13:21,545
She stayed with you
and wasted her life here.

212
00:13:21,625 --> 00:13:22,465
Shut up.

213
00:13:23,065 --> 00:13:24,225
Your mother…

214
00:13:24,745 --> 00:13:25,905
You have no right to judge.

215
00:13:25,985 --> 00:13:27,465
Then don't interfere with mine!

216
00:13:28,305 --> 00:13:31,385
Zhao, don't be angry with General Chu.

217
00:13:33,985 --> 00:13:35,105
General Chu,

218
00:13:35,185 --> 00:13:37,625
I know what you're worried about.

219
00:13:38,225 --> 00:13:39,585
Anyone who commands

220
00:13:40,105 --> 00:13:42,225
200,000 frontier troops

221
00:13:42,305 --> 00:13:44,465
would be worried that I pursued Zhao

222
00:13:44,545 --> 00:13:45,825
with ulterior motives.

223
00:13:45,905 --> 00:13:47,385
But I do not

224
00:13:47,905 --> 00:13:49,305
have any other motives.

225
00:13:49,825 --> 00:13:50,785
I only have a true heart.

226
00:13:52,745 --> 00:13:54,865
What's the value

227
00:13:56,145 --> 00:13:57,585
of a so-called true heart?

228
00:14:02,625 --> 00:14:03,825
Five years ago,

229
00:14:04,705 --> 00:14:06,145
I went to the Capital as a hostage.

230
00:14:07,305 --> 00:14:09,105
His Majesty gave me a mansion.

231
00:14:09,185 --> 00:14:10,905
To me,

232
00:14:11,905 --> 00:14:13,185
that is a reward

233
00:14:13,865 --> 00:14:15,105
as well as a shackle.

234
00:14:15,705 --> 00:14:17,065
I'm kept alive

235
00:14:17,585 --> 00:14:19,345
to counterbalance Xiaonan Prefecture.

236
00:14:20,185 --> 00:14:21,545
My father sent me there

237
00:14:22,305 --> 00:14:23,785
to protect our clan.

238
00:14:25,385 --> 00:14:26,825
I have no say in any of these.

239
00:14:27,665 --> 00:14:29,265
General Chu, you're right.

240
00:14:29,905 --> 00:14:32,145
No one would care about my heart.

241
00:14:34,145 --> 00:14:35,545
All these years,

242
00:14:36,065 --> 00:14:39,145
rumors in the Capital have never ceased.

243
00:14:40,065 --> 00:14:42,705
I'm used to tolerating them
and not arguing back.

244
00:14:43,905 --> 00:14:44,785
But it's different now.

245
00:14:47,505 --> 00:14:48,665
I love Zhao.

246
00:14:48,745 --> 00:14:51,545
I don't want my love for her
to be misunderstood.

247
00:14:53,225 --> 00:14:54,505
If I ever betray you,

248
00:14:57,945 --> 00:14:59,705
you could kill me now.

249
00:15:10,385 --> 00:15:11,545
Who are you trying to embarrass?

250
00:15:12,145 --> 00:15:14,265
Heir to the Lord of Xiaonan or my husband?

251
00:15:14,865 --> 00:15:16,785
If he really killed himself to prove it,

252
00:15:16,865 --> 00:15:17,745
would you be satisfied?

253
00:15:17,825 --> 00:15:19,705
We'll stop here on this matter!

254
00:15:23,665 --> 00:15:24,905
Your Highness,

255
00:15:26,345 --> 00:15:27,905
I suggest you go back.

256
00:15:31,865 --> 00:15:32,865
But General…

257
00:15:47,585 --> 00:15:48,745
General.

258
00:15:49,625 --> 00:15:50,465
Zhao!

259
00:16:11,625 --> 00:16:12,465
Where's my father?

260
00:16:13,625 --> 00:16:15,585
He's on a mission.
He sent me to see you off.

261
00:16:19,545 --> 00:16:20,385
No need.

262
00:16:21,465 --> 00:16:22,705
You're like him.

263
00:16:22,785 --> 00:16:23,785
You both despise Xun.

264
00:16:24,385 --> 00:16:25,905
When you don't mean it,

265
00:16:25,985 --> 00:16:27,265
you don't need to pretend.

266
00:16:30,385 --> 00:16:31,505
Whatever you think.

267
00:16:32,385 --> 00:16:34,505
But if one day you regret it,

268
00:16:34,585 --> 00:16:35,945
come back anytime.

269
00:16:41,505 --> 00:16:43,105
Master said that.

270
00:16:45,025 --> 00:16:47,985
Then please take my message
to General Chu.

271
00:16:50,745 --> 00:16:52,025
I won't regret it.

272
00:16:53,105 --> 00:16:54,905
Nor will I come back here.

273
00:17:11,424 --> 00:17:12,865
That farewell to my father

274
00:17:14,145 --> 00:17:15,625
was forever.

275
00:17:25,905 --> 00:17:28,345
THE 19TH YEAR OF TIANSHU

276
00:17:29,065 --> 00:17:30,625
After I returned to the Capital,

277
00:17:31,585 --> 00:17:33,425
I never stopped missing my father.

278
00:17:34,625 --> 00:17:36,545
It's not that he doesn't love me.

279
00:17:36,625 --> 00:17:38,465
He's just not good at showing his love.

280
00:17:39,585 --> 00:17:42,225
So, I often made his favorite jujube cakes

281
00:17:42,305 --> 00:17:44,825
and had them sent monthly to Yunzhong.

282
00:17:59,505 --> 00:18:02,385
Hang the red silk
and your wish will come true.

283
00:18:04,865 --> 00:18:08,225
But still, Father didn't approve
of this marriage.

284
00:18:08,905 --> 00:18:10,305
Two years later,

285
00:18:10,385 --> 00:18:12,545
Xiao Xun begged his father
to submit a memorial.

286
00:18:12,625 --> 00:18:14,625
They renounced their fief and troops.

287
00:18:14,705 --> 00:18:16,425
Finally, His Majesty granted the marriage.

288
00:18:22,385 --> 00:18:24,385
I just made a divination for you.

289
00:18:24,465 --> 00:18:26,665
A pair of phoenixes fly
and flap their feathers.

290
00:18:26,745 --> 00:18:27,705
Great luck.

291
00:18:28,305 --> 00:18:29,945
The eighth day of next month,
25 days from now,

292
00:18:30,025 --> 00:18:31,305
will be a rare lucky day.

293
00:18:31,385 --> 00:18:33,265
Everything will go smoothly.

294
00:18:35,985 --> 00:18:39,185
And anyway,
even if His Highness dared to hurt you,

295
00:18:39,265 --> 00:18:41,145
General Chu wouldn't let that happen.

296
00:18:41,985 --> 00:18:42,985
Look.

297
00:18:50,065 --> 00:18:52,585
Fu Jiu said he was sent
to deliver your dowry.

298
00:18:52,665 --> 00:18:53,865
But we all know

299
00:18:53,945 --> 00:18:56,985
your father sent him to stand up for you.

300
00:19:17,345 --> 00:19:19,185
Twenty five days later, it was
the 8th day of the 8th month,

301
00:19:19,265 --> 00:19:20,105
the 19th year of Tianshu.

302
00:19:20,745 --> 00:19:22,945
On my wedding night with Xiao Xun,

303
00:19:23,025 --> 00:19:25,025
rebels invaded the Capital.

304
00:19:25,105 --> 00:19:28,265
The whole city was ravaged by war.

305
00:19:31,465 --> 00:19:32,305
What happened?

306
00:19:32,385 --> 00:19:34,105
I heard the Third Prince
killed the Crown Prince

307
00:19:34,185 --> 00:19:35,665
and led a rebellion.

308
00:19:39,985 --> 00:19:40,985
Where's Xun?

309
00:19:41,065 --> 00:19:42,905
His Highness orders your protection.

310
00:19:42,985 --> 00:19:45,305
Please stay in the Chu Mansion.

311
00:19:48,065 --> 00:19:50,145
By order, you should stay here.

312
00:20:01,225 --> 00:20:03,785
Xun killed the Third Prince

313
00:20:05,305 --> 00:20:07,305
and ended this rebellion.

314
00:20:08,265 --> 00:20:10,105
An urgent message!

315
00:20:10,185 --> 00:20:11,905
The Emperor passed away!

316
00:20:11,985 --> 00:20:14,265
The Third Prince rebelled
and was executed!

317
00:20:14,345 --> 00:20:17,185
The Crown Prince
and the eldest imperial grandson died!

318
00:20:17,745 --> 00:20:20,185
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

319
00:20:20,265 --> 00:20:22,105
suppressed the rebellion!

320
00:20:22,185 --> 00:20:25,105
He'll take the throne,
by the late emperor's will!

321
00:20:31,385 --> 00:20:34,305
The Crown Prince died.
The Third Prince was executed.

322
00:20:35,305 --> 00:20:38,145
The imperial grandson Xiao Yu
died in the mutiny.

323
00:20:38,225 --> 00:20:39,305
The late emperor died.

324
00:20:39,905 --> 00:20:43,345
In the royal clan,
only Xiao Xun was left for the throne.

325
00:20:44,345 --> 00:20:47,425
Three days later, he ascended the throne

326
00:20:47,505 --> 00:20:49,425
and began his reign of the Anping era.

327
00:20:50,225 --> 00:20:52,905
This bloody fight for the throne
came to an end.

328
00:20:52,985 --> 00:20:56,185
It was known as the Anping Rebellion.

329
00:21:11,745 --> 00:21:13,785
TAIJI HALL

330
00:21:14,385 --> 00:21:15,745
Your Majesty,

331
00:21:15,825 --> 00:21:17,665
may you have longevity

332
00:21:17,745 --> 00:21:19,705
and a prosperous reign!

333
00:21:19,785 --> 00:21:21,945
Your Majesty,

334
00:21:22,025 --> 00:21:23,385
may you have longevity

335
00:21:23,465 --> 00:21:25,105
and a prosperous reign!

336
00:21:27,785 --> 00:21:29,345
Your Majesty,

337
00:21:29,425 --> 00:21:31,305
may you have longevity

338
00:21:31,385 --> 00:21:33,505
and a prosperous reign!

339
00:21:34,345 --> 00:21:36,025
Your Majesty,

340
00:21:36,105 --> 00:21:37,825
may you have longevity

341
00:21:37,905 --> 00:21:40,105
and a prosperous reign!

342
00:21:40,825 --> 00:21:44,385
Your Majesty, may you have longevity

343
00:21:44,465 --> 00:21:46,585
and a prosperous reign!

344
00:21:48,945 --> 00:21:50,465
I returned without a command.

345
00:21:50,545 --> 00:21:51,785
I know I'm guilty.

346
00:21:51,865 --> 00:21:53,865
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

347
00:21:55,545 --> 00:21:57,065
Don't say that, Father-in-law.

348
00:21:57,585 --> 00:21:58,905
You traveled day and night.

349
00:21:58,985 --> 00:22:00,785
Your love for your daughter

350
00:22:00,865 --> 00:22:02,425
is as clear as day.

351
00:22:02,505 --> 00:22:04,425
I… I'm quite gratified.

352
00:22:05,305 --> 00:22:06,745
I won't blame you.

353
00:22:06,825 --> 00:22:08,905
You once asked me

354
00:22:08,985 --> 00:22:12,225
about the value of my true heart.

355
00:22:12,305 --> 00:22:14,425
I was once a hostage.

356
00:22:14,505 --> 00:22:16,705
I know the pain of family separation.

357
00:22:16,785 --> 00:22:20,985
For Zhao,
I request that you stay in the Capital.

358
00:22:21,825 --> 00:22:25,385
As for the border,
I'll have everything arranged.

359
00:22:27,145 --> 00:22:30,185
I wonder if you will agree to my request.

360
00:22:36,665 --> 00:22:37,905
Your Majesty,

361
00:22:39,145 --> 00:22:40,785
I've devoted my life to ending the war.

362
00:22:41,585 --> 00:22:42,785
I have only one daughter.

363
00:22:43,425 --> 00:22:46,545
I treasure her more than my own life.

364
00:22:48,945 --> 00:22:52,745
Your Majesty,
please take good care of my daughter.

365
00:22:52,825 --> 00:22:55,065
My 200,000 frontier troops

366
00:22:55,585 --> 00:22:58,345
will also devote themselves to the good

367
00:22:59,345 --> 00:23:01,305
of our nation.

368
00:23:03,145 --> 00:23:04,265
Of course.

369
00:23:32,265 --> 00:23:33,465
Jiu,

370
00:23:35,425 --> 00:23:38,265
from this day on,
you'll stay here to protect Zhao.

371
00:23:39,505 --> 00:23:40,545
This is an order.

372
00:24:02,585 --> 00:24:04,745
VIRTUE OVER ALL LANDS

373
00:24:04,825 --> 00:24:06,145
After Xun's enthronement,

374
00:24:06,785 --> 00:24:08,705
Father hurried back to Yunzhong.

375
00:24:09,665 --> 00:24:11,025
He didn't attend my wedding.

376
00:24:12,265 --> 00:24:16,425
My marriage with Xun
went against Father's will after all.

377
00:24:16,505 --> 00:24:19,185
Take a look. Satisfied?

378
00:24:23,985 --> 00:24:26,225
Thank you, Your Majesty.

379
00:24:30,865 --> 00:24:34,145
Yesterday,
you suggested lower textile taxes.

380
00:24:34,225 --> 00:24:36,025
Can you explain that more clearly?

381
00:24:37,545 --> 00:24:39,025
As a thank-you for what I just did.

382
00:24:40,345 --> 00:24:42,745
Xun respected and loved me.

383
00:24:42,825 --> 00:24:44,385
An emperor like him

384
00:24:44,465 --> 00:24:46,545
often talked to me about state affairs.

385
00:24:47,065 --> 00:24:49,505
And he often carried out my suggestions

386
00:24:49,585 --> 00:24:51,625
to pacify the people.

387
00:24:52,505 --> 00:24:55,825
People praised him,
and their lives improved.

388
00:24:55,905 --> 00:24:59,905
I thought Father
might feel a little relieved.

389
00:25:08,185 --> 00:25:09,625
Every month, I wrote a letter to Father.

390
00:25:09,705 --> 00:25:10,545
ALL GOOD IN THE PALACE

391
00:25:10,625 --> 00:25:12,065
Yet he never wrote back.

392
00:25:13,265 --> 00:25:15,185
I wanted these letters of reassurance

393
00:25:15,945 --> 00:25:18,105
to soothe Father's worries.

394
00:25:21,945 --> 00:25:25,625
The Spring Equinox in the third year
of Anping was my 22nd birthday.

395
00:25:26,505 --> 00:25:28,265
Because I missed Father too much,

396
00:25:28,345 --> 00:25:30,985
Xun allowed me
to invite Father for my birthday

397
00:25:31,065 --> 00:25:33,745
and promised he'd be welcomed
as the Empress's father

398
00:25:33,825 --> 00:25:35,665
and get a corresponding residence.

399
00:25:36,305 --> 00:25:37,985
I was nervous.

400
00:25:38,065 --> 00:25:39,825
I was also eagerly anticipating it.

401
00:25:39,905 --> 00:25:40,945
VIRTUE OVER ALL LANDS

402
00:25:42,145 --> 00:25:43,305
Soldiers, disarm.

403
00:25:44,625 --> 00:25:47,025
General, will we really disarm?

404
00:25:47,105 --> 00:25:48,905
It's Zhao's birthday.

405
00:25:50,545 --> 00:25:51,465
Let's do it.

406
00:25:59,465 --> 00:26:01,945
Chu Ling, the Guard General,

407
00:26:02,025 --> 00:26:04,025
is summoned for an audience!

408
00:26:37,265 --> 00:26:41,105
Go, Zhao.
Later, I have a surprise for you.

409
00:26:44,105 --> 00:26:45,545
Thank you, Your Majesty.

410
00:26:46,625 --> 00:26:50,025
Greetings, Your Majesty.

411
00:26:55,465 --> 00:26:56,705
Father.

412
00:27:01,345 --> 00:27:03,065
You had a long trip, General.

413
00:27:05,625 --> 00:27:06,705
Read the edict.

414
00:27:07,425 --> 00:27:11,065
Edict for Chu Ling, the Guard General!

415
00:27:14,465 --> 00:27:17,625
Upon investigation,
Chu Ling, the Guard General,

416
00:27:18,145 --> 00:27:21,665
coerced the Emperor
and colluded with northern enemies.

417
00:27:22,185 --> 00:27:23,705
His brother Chu Lan

418
00:27:24,585 --> 00:27:28,025
poisoned the eldest imperial grandson
in the first year of Anping.

419
00:27:28,625 --> 00:27:32,225
The Chu clan shall be executed.

420
00:27:33,785 --> 00:27:35,025
Impossible!

421
00:27:35,665 --> 00:27:38,305
My father has always been loyal
without any improper desires.

422
00:27:38,385 --> 00:27:40,065
My uncle has been timid.

423
00:27:40,145 --> 00:27:42,345
In no way would he poison
the imperial grandson.

424
00:27:43,025 --> 00:27:43,865
You…

425
00:27:43,945 --> 00:27:45,145
You must be mistaken.

426
00:27:45,225 --> 00:27:47,185
Your Majesty. He is mistaken.

427
00:27:47,265 --> 00:27:49,305
Your Majesty, the other day,

428
00:27:49,385 --> 00:27:51,705
you said you'd give my father a mansion.

429
00:27:51,785 --> 00:27:53,065
Zhao,

430
00:27:54,065 --> 00:27:56,985
colluding with northern enemies
is a grave crime.

431
00:27:57,585 --> 00:27:59,585
Your father did something foolish.

432
00:27:59,665 --> 00:28:01,585
Even if you're the Empress,

433
00:28:02,105 --> 00:28:06,825
I have to answer
to all the people of my nation.

434
00:28:07,945 --> 00:28:09,465
In the first year of Anping,

435
00:28:09,545 --> 00:28:10,945
Your Majesty ascended the throne.

436
00:28:11,025 --> 00:28:12,785
Northern enemies
invaded Yunzhong at night.

437
00:28:12,865 --> 00:28:16,025
My father led 200,000 frontier troops
to defend the town without retreating!

438
00:28:16,625 --> 00:28:18,545
Now, he's accused
of colluding with enemies!

439
00:28:18,625 --> 00:28:19,705
Who?

440
00:28:20,305 --> 00:28:21,505
Who accused him?

441
00:28:21,585 --> 00:28:23,265
Who offered the evidence?

442
00:28:23,345 --> 00:28:25,305
The truth must be sorted out.

443
00:28:25,385 --> 00:28:26,985
Otherwise, it's a frame-up.

444
00:28:27,785 --> 00:28:31,225
The Empress is delirious
and spouting nonsense.

445
00:28:32,425 --> 00:28:33,265
Bring poisoned wine…

446
00:28:37,105 --> 00:28:38,305
and execute the Empress's father.

447
00:28:42,585 --> 00:28:44,945
Your Majesty. Your Majesty.

448
00:28:45,465 --> 00:28:48,065
Your Majesty. My father is innocent.

449
00:28:48,145 --> 00:28:49,585
He's innocent!

450
00:28:49,665 --> 00:28:52,065
Your Majesty, my father is innocent.

451
00:28:52,145 --> 00:28:53,425
He's innocent!

452
00:28:53,505 --> 00:28:54,985
I said, execute him!

453
00:28:56,305 --> 00:28:57,785
Xun! Xun!

454
00:28:59,985 --> 00:29:01,225
Xun.

455
00:29:03,385 --> 00:29:05,145
Xun. Xun.

456
00:29:05,745 --> 00:29:06,985
My father is innocent.

457
00:29:07,065 --> 00:29:08,625
Xun.

458
00:29:09,145 --> 00:29:10,945
Please spare my father. Xun.

459
00:29:22,185 --> 00:29:23,145
Changrong!

460
00:29:46,785 --> 00:29:48,865
You tread on the lives of frontier troops

461
00:29:48,945 --> 00:29:51,465
to appease your people
and secure your nation!

462
00:29:52,145 --> 00:29:55,945
So, this turns out to be your true heart.

463
00:29:56,025 --> 00:29:57,585
I've never dared to forget

464
00:29:58,385 --> 00:30:00,905
what you said on my enthronement day.

465
00:30:01,505 --> 00:30:02,505
Rest assured.

466
00:30:02,585 --> 00:30:04,665
Your 200,000 frontier troops

467
00:30:04,745 --> 00:30:06,225
will still devote themselves

468
00:30:06,305 --> 00:30:08,745
to my nation and me.

469
00:30:09,505 --> 00:30:12,345
General Chu Ling pulled out his blade
in front of His Majesty,

470
00:30:12,865 --> 00:30:14,105
intending to rebel.

471
00:30:14,185 --> 00:30:15,065
Execute him now!

472
00:30:24,385 --> 00:30:26,305
Father! Father!

473
00:30:26,385 --> 00:30:27,505
Father.

474
00:30:28,465 --> 00:30:29,385
Are you all right?

475
00:30:29,905 --> 00:30:31,825
Father. Sorry, Father.

476
00:30:33,265 --> 00:30:36,345
Father. Father. Sorry.

477
00:30:37,145 --> 00:30:39,025
I'm sorry, Father.

478
00:30:40,305 --> 00:30:41,305
I'm sorry.

479
00:30:41,825 --> 00:30:44,345
It's my fault. Father.

480
00:30:44,425 --> 00:30:46,905
Father, I'm sorry.

481
00:31:00,905 --> 00:31:03,025
-Xiao Xun, what do you want?
-Zhao.

482
00:31:03,105 --> 00:31:04,465
What are you going to do?

483
00:31:04,545 --> 00:31:06,385
-No.
-This is my surprise for you.

484
00:31:06,465 --> 00:31:08,225
No! No!

485
00:31:08,825 --> 00:31:10,345
Xiao Xun, let go of my father.

486
00:31:10,425 --> 00:31:12,385
No! No!

487
00:31:22,945 --> 00:31:26,625
The Empress shall be given poisoned wine

488
00:31:26,705 --> 00:31:29,385
for the sake of her filial devotion.

489
00:31:48,225 --> 00:31:49,665
I know you hate me.

490
00:31:52,385 --> 00:31:53,705
But you know that.

491
00:31:54,385 --> 00:31:55,345
In this case,

492
00:31:56,425 --> 00:31:58,425
if I hadn't convicted Chu Ling,

493
00:31:59,065 --> 00:32:01,545
how could I bring his frontier troops
under my control?

494
00:32:03,385 --> 00:32:05,825
Now, the whole nation is within my grasp,

495
00:32:06,825 --> 00:32:09,145
except for your father's troops!

496
00:32:09,225 --> 00:32:11,665
How can I secure this empire?

497
00:32:12,265 --> 00:32:13,585
Everyone in this nation says

498
00:32:14,785 --> 00:32:17,185
I wouldn't have succeeded
without a woman's help.

499
00:32:18,025 --> 00:32:21,345
They never see my hard reforms
over the past three years!

500
00:32:21,425 --> 00:32:23,065
They never see my diligent governance!

501
00:32:23,145 --> 00:32:25,185
They never see anything I've done!

502
00:32:25,265 --> 00:32:27,825
They can only see your father

503
00:32:27,905 --> 00:32:29,425
and his 200,000 frontier troops!

504
00:32:31,665 --> 00:32:32,865
But you said

505
00:32:34,625 --> 00:32:36,065
you didn't care.

506
00:32:36,865 --> 00:32:38,305
How could I not care?

507
00:32:39,505 --> 00:32:41,145
These 200,000 frontier troops

508
00:32:42,145 --> 00:32:43,865
were like a festering sore.

509
00:32:43,945 --> 00:32:45,065
Because of them,

510
00:32:45,145 --> 00:32:47,585
I couldn't sleep all night,
tormented by pain.

511
00:32:59,345 --> 00:33:01,065
I know you want to ask me

512
00:33:03,225 --> 00:33:05,305
why I did all this on your birthday.

513
00:33:07,025 --> 00:33:08,585
Because Zhao…

514
00:33:08,665 --> 00:33:10,625
Without your letter,

515
00:33:11,425 --> 00:33:12,705
he wouldn't have come back

516
00:33:14,065 --> 00:33:15,785
or disarmed.

517
00:33:16,545 --> 00:33:17,825
I wouldn't have managed

518
00:33:18,505 --> 00:33:19,865
to accuse him of rebelling

519
00:33:20,545 --> 00:33:22,585
even without his soldiers.

520
00:33:24,265 --> 00:33:27,785
Zhao, you're so clever.

521
00:33:28,625 --> 00:33:31,945
How could you not know

522
00:33:32,985 --> 00:33:36,985
your letter would make him
let down his guard?

523
00:33:37,585 --> 00:33:40,865
The 17th day of next month
will be your 22nd birthday.

524
00:33:40,945 --> 00:33:43,505
I drafted a decree to summon your father.

525
00:33:43,585 --> 00:33:45,185
As the Empress's father,

526
00:33:45,705 --> 00:33:47,385
he'll have a residence
in the imperial city.

527
00:33:48,505 --> 00:33:50,705
Write a letter to tell him about this.

528
00:33:51,785 --> 00:33:52,745
Why?

529
00:33:52,825 --> 00:33:55,265
Why did you do this to my clan?

530
00:33:55,345 --> 00:33:57,345
Why did you do this to me?

531
00:33:57,425 --> 00:33:59,345
Why?

532
00:34:14,505 --> 00:34:17,505
Actually, whether he did or didn't disarm,

533
00:34:18,905 --> 00:34:19,945
he'd end up the same.

534
00:34:22,905 --> 00:34:24,985
After I sent him away
on my enthronement day,

535
00:34:26,264 --> 00:34:27,665
I secretly had my men

536
00:34:27,744 --> 00:34:30,705
poison the jujube cakes
you sent to Yunzhong.

537
00:34:31,225 --> 00:34:34,304
From the Capital to Yunzhong,

538
00:34:34,385 --> 00:34:35,744
they were delivered monthly.

539
00:34:35,824 --> 00:34:37,304
CHU MANSION

540
00:34:37,985 --> 00:34:39,665
Chu Ling would be killed anyway.

541
00:34:40,385 --> 00:34:42,105
Not only by my blade,

542
00:34:43,065 --> 00:34:45,025
but also by his daughter's love.

543
00:35:10,985 --> 00:35:13,865
I'm going to kill you.

544
00:35:18,505 --> 00:35:20,025
Listen, Zhao.

545
00:35:21,785 --> 00:35:23,345
"In the third year of Anping,

546
00:35:25,305 --> 00:35:26,945
Chu clan was exterminated.

547
00:35:27,025 --> 00:35:29,025
Chu Ling, the Guard General,

548
00:35:30,105 --> 00:35:33,145
was guilty of treason and was executed.

549
00:35:34,025 --> 00:35:37,585
His daughter was so grieved

550
00:35:38,665 --> 00:35:40,305
that she hanged herself."

551
00:35:52,705 --> 00:35:54,185
Father is right.

552
00:35:54,705 --> 00:35:56,905
The Capital is a devouring cage.

553
00:35:57,665 --> 00:36:00,145
I wrongly believed his fake gentleness.

554
00:36:00,665 --> 00:36:03,465
I wrongly believed his fake loyalty.

555
00:36:03,545 --> 00:36:04,825
And I wrongly believed

556
00:36:05,585 --> 00:36:07,545
his insatiable ambition.

557
00:36:28,985 --> 00:36:30,465
It was him…

558
00:37:07,505 --> 00:37:09,985
I once had many choices in this life.

559
00:37:11,465 --> 00:37:13,865
But I was so willful and ignorant.

560
00:37:14,905 --> 00:37:16,905
I made a wrong choice every time.

561
00:37:18,585 --> 00:37:20,745
I got my father killed.

562
00:37:22,105 --> 00:37:24,025
I ruined my whole clan.

563
00:37:25,305 --> 00:37:26,545
Father!

564
00:37:29,385 --> 00:37:31,465
I got myself killed too.

565
00:37:43,785 --> 00:37:44,665
VOID AND BEING AS ONE

566
00:38:01,105 --> 00:38:04,505
A pair of phoenixes fly
and flap their feathers.

567
00:38:04,585 --> 00:38:05,545
Great luck.

568
00:38:08,025 --> 00:38:09,745
THE 19TH YEAR OF TIANSHU

569
00:38:23,105 --> 00:38:25,025
HEART AT PEACE, LET THINGS BE

570
00:38:25,105 --> 00:38:26,505
Not to mention
the glorious dress and coronet,

571
00:38:26,585 --> 00:38:28,225
you even deserve the 12 ornaments
of imperial Robes.

572
00:38:28,745 --> 00:38:30,265
But I do not have any other motives.

573
00:38:30,345 --> 00:38:31,265
I only have a true heart.

574
00:38:31,345 --> 00:38:32,185
I love Zhao.

575
00:38:32,265 --> 00:38:34,705
I don't want my love for her
to be misunderstood.

576
00:38:49,545 --> 00:38:51,025
Miss.

577
00:38:51,665 --> 00:38:53,305
What year is it now?

578
00:38:53,385 --> 00:38:55,665
You're so rude. Let go of me.

579
00:38:56,185 --> 00:38:58,825
It's the 14th day of the seventh month,
the 19th year of Tianshu!

580
00:38:59,585 --> 00:39:02,145
-Miss, don't do this. Let go.
-The 19th year of Tianshu?

581
00:39:02,225 --> 00:39:03,465
Don't you dare bully her!

582
00:39:03,545 --> 00:39:04,665
Don't be ridiculous.

583
00:39:04,745 --> 00:39:06,585
Just now, she almost hurt my hand.

584
00:39:07,785 --> 00:39:08,785
-Miss.
-Odd.

585
00:39:08,865 --> 00:39:09,825
Are you fine?

586
00:39:11,185 --> 00:39:12,625
You're real.

587
00:39:13,705 --> 00:39:16,145
I just went away to fetch red silk.

588
00:39:16,225 --> 00:39:17,505
Miss, what happened to you?

589
00:39:22,185 --> 00:39:23,985
I'm still alive.

590
00:39:24,065 --> 00:39:25,385
Did you lose your mind,

591
00:39:26,065 --> 00:39:28,225
or are you possessed?

592
00:39:28,745 --> 00:39:30,945
Shall I take you back
and wash you with pomelo leaves?

593
00:39:33,225 --> 00:39:34,065
I'll go get His Highness.

594
00:39:34,145 --> 00:39:35,145
Zhao.

595
00:39:48,585 --> 00:39:49,425
Now I'm the Emperor.

596
00:39:49,505 --> 00:39:52,065
I'll never make you
shed tears because of farewells.

597
00:39:52,145 --> 00:39:53,385
You only need to dress yourself up

598
00:39:53,465 --> 00:39:55,305
and make yourself beautiful.

599
00:40:06,545 --> 00:40:07,865
What's wrong, Zhao?

600
00:40:08,625 --> 00:40:09,545
Why are you crying?

601
00:40:09,625 --> 00:40:11,305
I'm going to kill you!

602
00:40:11,385 --> 00:40:12,665
You killed my father.

603
00:40:12,745 --> 00:40:13,585
I'll kill you!

604
00:40:14,185 --> 00:40:15,185
Miss.

605
00:40:15,265 --> 00:40:16,265
I'll kill you.

606
00:40:16,345 --> 00:40:17,825
I will.

607
00:40:29,945 --> 00:40:32,505
Thank you, Fu Jiu, for the dowry.

608
00:40:32,585 --> 00:40:36,265
Recently,
she has been nervous about the wedding.

609
00:40:36,345 --> 00:40:37,185
So…

610
00:40:37,785 --> 00:40:40,305
The dowry's been delivered. I'll leave.

611
00:40:57,665 --> 00:41:01,025
Today, Zhao acted strangely toward me.

612
00:41:01,625 --> 00:41:03,705
What on earth happened

613
00:41:04,945 --> 00:41:06,585
that changed her like that?

614
00:41:07,185 --> 00:41:09,825
The bell in Sanqing Temple
accidentally fell.

615
00:41:09,905 --> 00:41:11,065
Was she scared then?

616
00:41:11,665 --> 00:41:12,705
No.

617
00:41:14,385 --> 00:41:15,625
What she said was…

618
00:41:16,145 --> 00:41:17,385
You killed my father.

619
00:41:17,465 --> 00:41:18,985
I'm going to kill you!

620
00:41:20,425 --> 00:41:24,105
I've never shown hostility
toward Chu Ling.

621
00:41:24,185 --> 00:41:26,465
Why did Zhao suddenly say
something like that?

622
00:41:27,105 --> 00:41:30,425
Could she have known my plan?

623
00:41:52,225 --> 00:41:53,385
How did this happen?

624
00:41:57,225 --> 00:41:59,785
Miss, what happened to you?

625
00:42:00,385 --> 00:42:02,145
Shall I make a divination for you?

626
00:42:04,585 --> 00:42:05,465
Oh no.

627
00:42:05,545 --> 00:42:06,665
I'm not capable enough.

628
00:42:06,745 --> 00:42:08,305
I'll send for a Taoist master.

629
00:42:08,385 --> 00:42:09,345
Le,

630
00:42:12,425 --> 00:42:14,345
the 8th day of the 8th month this year

631
00:42:15,585 --> 00:42:17,785
is the wedding day for Xiao Xun and me.

632
00:42:17,865 --> 00:42:19,065
Right?

633
00:42:20,745 --> 00:42:22,665
His Majesty set this date.

634
00:42:23,985 --> 00:42:25,505
So, this is all real.

635
00:42:27,305 --> 00:42:28,345
Oh, you're bleeding.

636
00:42:28,425 --> 00:42:29,745
Don't you feel the pain?

637
00:42:32,585 --> 00:42:33,465
Yeah.

638
00:42:34,545 --> 00:42:36,105
When it hurts, it's real.

639
00:42:36,865 --> 00:42:38,145
It's real.

640
00:42:39,505 --> 00:42:40,345
Oh, dear.

641
00:42:40,425 --> 00:42:41,945
Don't scare me.

642
00:42:42,465 --> 00:42:44,585
What on earth happened?
Could you please tell me?

643
00:42:45,585 --> 00:42:47,345
Why are you crying again?

644
00:42:50,985 --> 00:42:54,065
Le, go make some calming soup for me.

645
00:42:57,465 --> 00:42:58,505
All right.

646
00:43:44,225 --> 00:43:45,425
Who are you?

647
00:43:45,505 --> 00:43:47,425
I am you.

648
00:43:48,545 --> 00:43:50,625
I'm all your resentment

649
00:43:50,705 --> 00:43:51,985
and all your hatred.

650
00:43:53,185 --> 00:43:55,825
I'm the blade you brought back
from the underworld.

651
00:43:56,625 --> 00:43:58,105
Just like the two sides

652
00:43:58,625 --> 00:44:00,825
of the robe.

653
00:44:02,745 --> 00:44:03,985
How did I come back to life?

654
00:44:04,065 --> 00:44:06,065
It's a heaven-sent opportunity.

655
00:44:06,145 --> 00:44:08,945
You can take your revenge.

656
00:44:13,185 --> 00:44:14,265
It's not easy

657
00:44:15,465 --> 00:44:16,985
to kill Xiao Xun.

658
00:44:17,625 --> 00:44:19,865
He's been scheming all the time,

659
00:44:19,945 --> 00:44:22,385
determined to be a decent gentleman.

660
00:44:22,465 --> 00:44:24,545
I have no chips to bring him down.

661
00:44:28,385 --> 00:44:32,505
My priority is to stay alive.

662
00:44:34,985 --> 00:44:37,345
Only when I'm alive can I save myself

663
00:44:37,425 --> 00:44:38,665
and save my father.

664
00:44:43,305 --> 00:44:44,545
Rest assured.

665
00:44:45,305 --> 00:44:48,185
I'll get revenge on Xiao Xun
in the same way

666
00:44:49,425 --> 00:44:51,985
he ruined the Chu family.

667
00:44:53,785 --> 00:45:00,625
I won't allow
even the slightest difference.

668
00:47:34,665 --> 00:47:36,985
Subtitle translation by:
